  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "Activity 1.1: Procurement and distribution of 7,000 composite packets of Vegetable seeds\r\n\r\nGovernment (MOAD) has planned to distribute Wheat (16 ha), maize (16 ha) and lentil seeds (2 metric tons) within the targeted project areas.\r\n\r\nActivity 1.2: Procurement and distribution of 200,000 nos. of Fingerlings plus fish feed\r\n\r\nActivity 1.3: Procurement and distribution of 200 nos. of. Metal Bins \r\n\r\nActivity 1.4: Procurement and distribution of 1200 HHs. of Hermetic bags \r\n\r\nActivity 1.5: Procurement and distribution of 40 set of Threshers \r\n\r\nActivity 2.1: Procurement and installation of Treadle pump to irrigate vegetable farming\r\n\r\nActivity 2.2: Procurement and installation of Shallow tube well installation (drip irrigation) in the sand casted areas to irrigate wheat, pulses and vegetable cultivation\r\n\r\nActivity 2.3: Rehabilitation of damaged/sand deposited fish ponds\r\n\r\nActivity 2.4: Spot repair of farmer's managed small scale irrigation schemes  \r\n\r\nActivity 2.5: Protection of the human settlement through sport repair of river embankment."
    },
    "ne": null
  },
